<h1>Young Musicians’ Course</h1>

<p>The Young Musicians’ Course provides an ideal environment for children to be motivated by each other as they learn important musical skills including keyboard and piano performance, ensemble playing, improvisation, singing and reading of music.</p>

<p>Our passionate and highly qualified teachers will create a sense of discovery as they inspire your child towards a life-long love of music.</p>

<h2>Curriculum</h2>

<p>
	<strong>Keyboard & Piano Performance</strong><br/>
	<strong>Aural Training</strong><br/>
	<strong>Ensemble Playing</strong><br/>
	<strong>Improvisation</strong><br/>
	<strong>Singing</strong><br/>
	<strong>Reading</strong>
</p>

<h2>Course Structure</h2>

<p>
	<strong>Lesson duration:</strong> 1 hour per week during school terms<br/>
	<strong>Course duration:</strong> Three years<br/>
	<strong>Class size:</strong> 6-12 students
</p>


